00:00:07.310 --> 00:00:09.350
we need to look at the speed report.

00:00:10.390 --> 00:00:16.500
Speed reports show us how different
request took in our app or site.

00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:20.190
You may want to track how quickly the
screens for each new level of the game

00:00:20.190 --> 00:00:25.370
load, or how fast search result have
been brought back to the user's page.

00:00:25.370 --> 00:00:29.080
You could also toggle between
different version of this report, and

00:00:29.080 --> 00:00:34.020
I'll show you what to gain from the
distribution, and the overlay reports.

