By the way, this report is important
enough to be taken to the dashboard so

00:00:39.430 --> 00:00:42.170
you can face it on a daily basis.

00:00:42.170 --> 00:00:45.870
In my last startup,
we also sent it on a weekly basis.

00:00:45.870 --> 00:00:50.580
So we could see if and
how we improving after each new version.

00:00:51.990 --> 00:00:56.300
The main metrics that you gain from
this reports is definitely to see

00:00:56.300 --> 00:00:59.560
what is the average load
time of each and every page.

00:00:59.560 --> 00:01:02.960
And here you can see that I
definitely had a problem with my site

00:01:02.960 --> 00:01:04.870
